name: Wedding Photography
description: We will create an atmosphere specially for you to take the best photos ever! Wedding photos will be a memory about your happy day for all your life. Wedding is a day when family starts and photos should be the most beautiful. After the wedding day it usually takes from 10 to 30 days to provide you with ready photos.

name: Lifestyle Photography
description: We will make a photo session describing your lifestyle and personality. Photos will be a memory about your happy day for all your life. Photo session can be organized in the studio or somewhere in beautiful place where your celebration will take place. We have 10 years experience of shooting and have many ideas and tips to make this day unforgettable.

name: Studio Photography
description: Studio photo sessions are basically for aspiring models,actors to create their portfolios. Other people can also book this package they want to take professional portait photos. Nowadays studio photo sessions are getting very popular as more and more people wants to have their photos taken by professionals.
